titleNullable: Cat vs Dog Image Classification, making prediction
descriptionNullable:
Welcome to the "Cat vs Dog Image Classification" dataset, a curated collection designed for training and evaluating machine learning and deep learning models to distinguish between images of cats and dogs. The dataset is organized into three main subfolders: "single_prediction," "test_set," and "training_set," each containing meticulously labeled images for seamless model development.
